Good morning,

I thought this article from Patrick McKenzie ( https://www.bitsaboutmoney.c=
om/archive/banking-in-very-uncertain-times/ ) was a very good addition to t=
he discussion around the ongoing bank issues; it takes a broader view of wh=
at is happening than just the specifics around Silicon Valley Bank.

Meanwhile, over the last few days there have been three major AI-related de=
velopments, and the week is not yet over.

On to the update:

